# Burger Ordering System üçî

A simple Java console application that simulates a burger ordering system.

## Features
- Create regular and deluxe burgers
- Add multiple toppings
- Calculate total meal price
- Itemized order printing

## OOP Concepts Used
- Encapsulation
- Inheritance
- Polymorphism
- Method overriding

## Project Structure
- Item ‚Äì base class for menu items
- Burger ‚Äì extends Item
- DeluxeBurger ‚Äì special burger with free toppings
- MealOrder ‚Äì manages a full meal
- Main ‚Äì application entry point

## How to Run
1. Open the project in IntelliJ IDEA
2. Run `Main.java`
3. View output in the console

